::Ramulus::

Ramulus takes out a scanner, walking toward DeathScythe. He looks down at the 
scanner, looking up in several seconds.

"He's out cold," he says to SnowCat, "He's too big to bring with us, I think 
we should leave him here."

Ramulus suddenly spins around, his scanners picking up another bot (Rattrap).

"We're not alone," he says, taking out his gun and walking slowly toward the 
edge of the clearing.
